Third Department,

September, 1944.

(September 13, 1944.) In the Matter of the Claim of Humbert J. Campana, Respondent, against Prudential Insurance Company of America et al., Appellants. State Industrial Board, Respondent.

Motion for reargument denied. Motion for leave

to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied, without costs. [See 267 App. Div. 1007.] All concur.
